data.title: Football Players Data
data.meta_description: Football Players Data - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document contains a list of 113 soccer players ranked by their overall potential and value. It includes each player's ID number, name, age, nationality, overall potential rating, club potential rating, estimated market value, and weekly wage. Some of the top ranked players include Lionel Messi, Cristiano Ronaldo, Neymar Jr., Kevin De Bruyne, and Mohamed Salah.
